        "title": "证监会发布“并购重组新规”：鼓励上市公司加强产业整合，大幅简化并购审核流程",
        "uri": "https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3728769"
      },
      "author": {
        "avatar": "https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/714916ad-9609-4245-94b4-dfe9518a63c3",
        "display_name": "万小婷",
        "id": 120000003969,
        "is_followed": false,
